title: Little Dorrit  -  Charles Dickens   (BBC 2001)
description:
Charles Dickens - Little Dorrit - Full Cast Drama
BBC Radio 4 - Classic Serial
Broadcast: 2001-04-22 to 2001-05-20



Little Dorrit is a work of satire on the shortcomings of the government and society of the period.The prison in this story is the Marshalsea where the author's own father had been imprisoned.

With Ian McKellan and  co-starring John Wood, Julian Wadham and Margaret Tyzack.
